summary: So thank you to The Russos and everyone that was part of this movie from the people that clean sets to Kevin Feige. I can’t wait...
body:
The more I read reviews fans made of Endgame, the more I realize what a hard job the Russos had…

I mean there’s at least around 60 Marvel characters in Endgame and more than 100 million people saw the movie in the opening weekend! In one weekend over 100 million people saw it!!

100 million humans that probably have a favorite character, favorite marvel movie, favorite relationship, favorite friendship, favorite siblings and favorite villains, hell even favorite theories. Satisfying everyone’s wants and fantasies for their characters it’s an impossible job, and I think the Russos did a good job, the movie was a ride, it made me laugh, tense, mad and cry. I think it was a beautiful ending for a wonderful era but a beautiful beginning too.

So thank you to The Russos and everyone that was part of this movie from the people that clean sets to Kevin Feige. I can’t wait to see where you take us next.
